{"type":"message","id":"53160977","parentId":"d8fc6343","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:27:21.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我目前安装了以下技能：\n\n## 搜索与信息\n- **skill-finder-cn** - 查找和安装 ClawHub Skills\n- **openclaw-tavily-search** - Tavily 网页搜索\n- **multi-search-engine** - 17 个搜索引擎集成（含中文和全球引擎）\n- **news-summary** - 新闻摘要和每日简报\n\n## 飞书/Lark 集成\n- **feishu-doc** - 飞书云文档读写\n- **feishu-drive** - 飞书云空间文件管理\n- **feishu-wiki** - 飞书知识库\n- **feishu-perm** - 飞书权限管理\n- **feishu-bitable** - 飞书多维表格\n- **feishu-calendar** - 飞书日历与日程\n- **feishu-task** - 飞书任务管理\n- **feishu-im-read** - 飞书消息读取\n- **feishu-create-doc** - 创建飞书文档\n- **feishu-update-doc** - 更新飞书文档\n- **feishu-fetch-doc** - 获取飞书文档内容\n- **feishu-troubleshoot** - 飞书问题排查\n\n## 自动化与工具\n- **browser-automation** - 浏览器自动化\n- **desktop-control-win** - Windows 桌面控制\n- **cron-mastery** - 定时任务管理\n- **office-automation-test** - 办公自动化测试\n\n## 自我提升\n- **self-improving** - 自我反思与学习\n- **proactivity** - 主动性与任务跟进\n- **skill-vetter** - Skill 安全审查\n- **memory-setup** - 记忆系统配置\n\n需要我详细介绍某个技能的功能吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":11022,"output":387,"cacheRead":26624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38033,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773736027396}}
